Class RpmVerifyFileItem

  • java.lang.Object
    • jp.go.aist.six.oval.model.sc.ItemType

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    OvalObject

    public class RpmVerifyFileItem
extends ItemType
    This item stores the verification results of the individual files in an RPM similar to what is produced by the rpm -V command.
